      "text": "Open with the Excalidraw VS Code extension and draw the agentic loop shown in ARCHITECTURE.md §3.\n\nFlow:\n  1. User query\n  2. AI Agent node (DeepSeek V4 Flash)\n  3. Tool pick: search_kb / search_ephemeral / web_lookup / ask_clarifying_question\n  4. Voyage embed → pgvector kNN → Voyage rerank → top 5 chunks\n  5. Synthesize answer with DeepSeek V4 Flash\n  6. Gemini self-check → faithfulness score\n  7. IF score < 0.7 → retry with DeepSeek V4 Pro\n  8. Return answer + sources + faithfulness",
